title: [LFM] Diamond 5's Team Looking for Jungler (Diamond + )
body: Hey everyone, our team is looking for a jungler for ranked 5's. We are currently ranked diamond 5 and haven't played since our old jungler had to quit the team due to family issues. If you're interested please add me so we can discuss trial times etc.

replies.body: Bump, our team is once again looking for a diamond and above jungler. Add me and message me in game to organise a trial time. Thanks.
yeah im keen lads ill add u now
